					<p>Mr. Andrew Jenkinson is a general surgeon in Harley Street, London specialising in Bariatric and
						Laparoscopic procedures. His interests include surgery for weight loss and diabetes, acid reflux
						disease, gallstones, hernia repair and surgical emergencies. He is a Fellow of the Royal College
						of Surgeons and holds a Master of Surgery title for his research thesis. He is a member of the
						British Obesity and Metabolic Surgery Society, the International Federation of Surgery for
						Obesity, the Association of Upper GI Surgeons and the American Society for Metabolic and
						Bariatric Surgery.</p>
